title: AIMS, Kabul City Land Use, Afghanistan, 2005 - Fields Only
name: AIMS, Kabul City Land Use, Afghanistan, 2005 - Fields Only
description:
Abstract:
        This layer depicts various type of land use in Kabul city. These land use includes the following, Airport, Cemetery, Agriculture Fields, Lakes, Parks, Stadiums, Urban Areas and Rural Areas. These layers were digitized from IKONOS satellite imagery (2000-2002) at 1:5,000 scale both from one meter resolution (most of Kabul) and 2.5 meter resolution (outside of Kabul). The shapefile has polygon topology and was created in ArcView 3.x shapefile. 
    Purpose:
        This layer provides a ready reference for Kabul city land use types, which could be used for many purposes such as depicting geographic locations (Land marks) and making further analysis using various types of land uses.
